{"id":7306,"date":"2021-11-24T15:59:19","date_gmt":"2021-11-24T08:59:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?p=7306"},"modified":"2024-07-15T08:46:37","modified_gmt":"2024-07-15T01:46:37","slug":"bastille-day-celebration","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/bastille-day-celebration\/","title":{"rendered":"Bastille Day Celebration"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Bastille-Day-6-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/be846cd379e0220ecdbb7022e8d24081_Bastille-Day-6-1-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/be846cd379e0220ecdbb7022e8d24081_Bastille-Day-6-1-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/be846cd379e0220ecdbb7022e8d24081_Bastille-Day-6-1-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/be846cd379e0220ecdbb7022e8d24081_Bastille-Day-6-1-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Bastille-Day-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bastille Day 6\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47lked41 fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47lked42 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47lked46 fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/2920c7f2b4464a229d189ea6bcb3abf9_Reflections-Restaurant-Logo-PNG-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Reflections Restaurant Logo-PNG\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-5dvno8tp fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">THE TASTES OF FRENCH<\/h3>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 561px;top: -11.125px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-68h42uts fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>SAVOUR 25% OFF for ALL GUESTS<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Embark on a culinary odyssey through the lively gastronomic tapestry of France as we celebrate Bastille Day in the Heart of Saigon.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Unveiling an authentic array of classic French dishes, inaugurate your journey with the traditional indulgence of Escargot with Garlic Herb Butter, followed by the indulgent and heartwarming French Onion Soup with Cheese Croutons. Then, relish the succulent beef tenderloin harmoniously complemented by the lavish richness of Foie Gras.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Conclude your dining soiree with the exquisite Mille Feuille Vanilla pastry, renowned for its delicate flavors and countless layers, all while taking in the breathtaking cityscape from the elegant setting of Reflections Restaurant.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Bastille Day 5-course menu is proposed from VND 1,590,000++ per person<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Enhance your experience with paired wine at VND 1,390,000++ per person<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Offer applies from 14th July to 21st July, from 17:30 &ndash; 22:00<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fjrv0 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fk27s fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5flgsa buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Reflections-French-5-course-scaled.jpg\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-t